ation delivery system around which a world/campus-wide' b'information system (cwis) can readily be constructed. while' b'providing a delivery vehicle for local information, gopher' b'facilitates access to other gopher and information servers' b'throughout the world.' b'' b'-------------------------------------------------------------------' b'q1: where can i get gopher software?' b'' b'a1: via anonymous ftp to boombox.micro.umn.edu. look in the directory' b'/pub/gopher' b'' b'--------------------------------------------------------------------' b'q2: what do i need to access gopher?' b'' b'a2: you will need a gopher "client" program that runs on your local pc' b'or workstation' b'' b'there are clients for the following systems. the directory' b'following the name is the location of the client on the anonymous' b'ftp site boombox.micro.umn.edu in the directory' b'/pub/gopher.' b'' b'unix curses emacs /pub/gopher/unix/gopher1.12.tar.z' b'xwindows (athena) /pub/gopher/unix/xgopher1.2.tar.z' b'xwindows (motif) /pub/gopher/unix/moog' b'xwindows (xview) /pub/gopher/unix/xvgopher' b'macintosh hypercard /pub/gopher/macintosh-turbogopher/old-versions b'macintosh application /pub/gopher/macintosh-turbogopher b'dos w/clarkson driver /pub/gopher/pc_client/' b'nextstep /pub/gopher/next/' b'vm/cms /pub/gopher/rice_cms/ or /pub/gopher/viegopher/' b'vms /pub/gopher/vms/' b'os/2 2.0\t /pub/gopher/os2/' b'mvs/xa /pub/gopher/mvs/' b'' b'many other clients and servers have been developed by others, the' b'following is an attempt at a comprehensive list.' b'' b'a microsoft windows winsock client "the gopher book"' b'sunsite.unc.edu:/pub/micro/pc-stuff/ms-windows/winsock/goph_tbk.zip' b'' b'a macintosh application, "macgopher".' b'ftp.cc.utah.edu:/pub/gopher/macintosh b'' b'another macintosh application, "gopherapp".' b'ftp.bio.indiana.edu:/util/gopher/gopherapp b'' b'a port of the unix curses client for dos with pc/tcp' b'oac.hsc.uth.tmc.edu:/public/dos/misc/dosgopher.exe' b'' b'a port 